main event: A civilian pilot observed a string of light while flying over Devils Lake.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on 16 July 1960., The observation was made at 0213 EST on 17 July 1960., The sighting was reported by S/Sgt Rodrlques of the 735th Radar Squadron., The object was described as very bright., The conclusion suggested it could have been a balloon, but there was insufficient data for evaluation.
